leadership_approach|process_results_vision_people|strength_1|1|Dependable coordination|When this pattern is working well, Process gives leadership a steadier way to organise work. Steps, standards, and responsibilities become clearer, so people can act with less confusion and less rework.|process|active|leadership_approach::process_results_vision_people::strength_1
leadership_approach|process_results_vision_people|strength_2|2|Structure that turns into action|Process and Results together can make structure practical rather than heavy. The strength is that standards, steps, and responsibilities are connected to decisions and visible progress.|results|active|leadership_approach::process_results_vision_people::strength_2
leadership_approach|process_results_vision_people|strength_3|3|Range through stronger trust after Vision|Vision can broaden the first two signals before People is brought in deliberately. People adds range when the pattern has movement, structure, or direction and now needs better communication around the human impact. It can make progress more sustainable because people understand their part in the work.|people|active|leadership_approach::process_results_vision_people::strength_3
