leadership_approach|process_results_people_vision|strength_2|2|Structure that turns into action|Process and Results together can make structure practical rather than heavy. The strength is that standards, steps, and responsibilities are connected to decisions and visible progress.|results|active|leadership_approach::process_results_people_vision::strength_2
leadership_approach|process_results_people_vision|strength_3|3|Range through wider direction after People|People can broaden the first two signals before Vision is brought in deliberately. Vision adds range when the pattern is handling people, structure, or delivery and now needs a stronger reason for the work. It can lift the decision from the immediate task to meaning and future consequence.|vision|active|leadership_approach::process_results_people_vision::strength_3
