leadership_approach|process_vision_results_people|strength_2|2|Structure with a reason|Process and Vision together can make change feel more coherent. The strength is that future direction is given a working path, so the bigger frame can be translated into organised action.|vision|active|leadership_approach::process_vision_results_people::strength_2
leadership_approach|process_vision_results_people|strength_3|3|Range through stronger trust after Results|Results can broaden the first two signals before People is brought in deliberately. People adds range when the pattern has movement, structure, or direction and now needs better communication around the human impact. It can make progress more sustainable because people understand their part in the work.|people|active|leadership_approach::process_vision_results_people::strength_3
